    <Section title='About'>
      <p class='text-muted-foreground'>
        Fullstack developer that specializes in React.
        <br />
        Sometimes dabble in .Net Core.
        <br />
        Currently enjoy developing in a bun monorepo.
      </p>
    </Section>
